{"tid":1821739,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共前統戰部官員美出書 撕破騙局","createTime":"2020-01-12T13:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T16:39:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0079f6a2e562d666b71fdb2247479c766752c469","tid":1821739,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200112/BYDZISWZILY56WBVPCLQXJSRXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200112%2FBYDZISWZILY56WBVPCLQXJSRXU%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXeExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=7e57d434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200112%2FBYDZISWZILY56WBVPCLQXJSRXU%2F&h=d1bb7ee4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200112/BYDZISWZILY56WBVPCLQXJSRXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共前統戰部官員美出書 撕破騙局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200112/large/1578759083_c81d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578759083_c81d.gif&h=4191bdc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n程干遠（右圖）所著的《中共統戰部揭秘》英文版。<br />\n<br />\n曾任中共南京市委統戰部官員、現居美國的法學家程干遠所著《中共統戰部揭秘》英文版在美國出版，近日在華盛頓舉行首發儀式。程在會上以自己親身經歷，直指中共的「統一戰線」(簡稱統戰)是政治騙局，呼籲國際社會警惕。主辦新書發佈會的美國人權組織「公民力量」主席楊建利指，在當前中共不斷擴大海外影響力背景下，程的書對海外了解中共統戰非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n助海外了解統戰<br />\n<br />\n程干遠的《中共統戰部揭秘》中文版早年已出。該書通過大量事實，講述中共統戰部門如何對目標人物進行統戰，如何對民主黨派和宗教界進行控制等。程指中共的統戰「說白了就是政治詐騙。特別在今天新形勢下，中共統戰不但沒削弱，反而不斷加強。」程指，習近平上台後大搞統戰，成立統戰工作領導小組，習親自當組長。「中共大統戰和大外宣結合，正在走向世界，包括美國。」<br />\n<br />\n86歲的程干遠原籍安徽績溪，與中共前總書記胡錦濤同籍，16歲參加解放軍任汽車兵，曾赴北韓參加抗美援朝；1954年回國後，獲當局保送入復旦大學法律系就讀；畢業後被分到中央人民政府內務部(60年代撤銷，業務併入民政部和公安部)，後調至中共南京市委統戰部，從事統戰工作長達十年。退休後赴美定居。曾出版回憶錄《親歷韓戰》、《中共統戰部揭秘》中文版等。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"73dc1337efa3a03c3fc5dde1d1985e9482b97c9e","tid":1821739,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"Puah<br />\n要揾人研究下"},{"pid":"8a43e02c42202fd0efa0556c06c562f0824f0906","tid":1821739,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月13日 星期一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">鰂魚涌:香港保險㒰人職工會街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1200-1500<br />\n地點 ：太古坊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">維園:香港制藥及醫療儀器業職工總會街站</span><br />\n時間 ： 1230-1400<br />\n地點 ：維園圓形噴水池<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">中環:119天下制裁大遊行</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月19日 星期日<br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點 ：遮打道 至 銅鑼灣SOGO<br />\n(*不反對通知書申請中)"},{"pid":"d3043df013003a8f7185f6151574e75bccd6516e","tid":1821739,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"被自殺了"},{"pid":"1a985334d449c78ebda7c8201a1b74d21532e276","tid":1821739,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198e50ad6058406c9e4a9c26277cbec49228511e","tid":1821739,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"想買"},{"pid":"1e8afecd1a7f8e52024c0b472496593626823dca","tid":1821739,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:26:51.000Z","msg":"中文版有冇書局入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3299e159d2acc1708c36787e1d9a8b0d6518b861","tid":1821739,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/history-mystery-united-front-work-department-20170622/3912625.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fhistory-mystery-united-front-work-department-20170622%2F3912625.html&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXeExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=54e3de66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/